Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我來晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜託妳了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要把開膛手傑克…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.45,0:00:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 出局！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍微放輕鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,之後我們可是要當誘餌的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
